Why?

00:58:43.690 --> 00:58:45.310
Because measurement
is the only way

00:58:45.310 --> 00:58:49.890
you can eventually make
decisions at some point.

00:58:49.890 --> 00:58:53.467
Doesn't matter how
committed you are.

00:58:53.467 --> 00:58:55.300
At some point, you have
to make a trade off.

00:58:55.300 --> 00:58:57.420
Should I do this or do that?

00:58:57.420 --> 00:59:02.830
I love the talk from
Seventh Generation.

00:59:02.830 --> 00:59:04.130
I thought it was great.

00:59:04.130 --> 00:59:07.780
Should you should
use these bags that

00:59:07.780 --> 00:59:10.750
