01:00:25.390 --> 01:00:28.100
and they did life cycle
analysis of materials.

01:00:28.100 --> 01:00:30.290
And they tried to
inform their decisions

01:00:30.290 --> 01:00:32.710
as best as possible--
measurements

01:00:32.710 --> 01:00:35.150
so people can make the decisions
of the moment of making

01:00:35.150 --> 01:00:37.250
that trade off.

01:00:37.250 --> 01:00:41.350
That was the idea of getting
carbon life cycles thinking

01:00:41.350 --> 01:00:43.550
