So keep some of
these things in mind

01:21:50.160 --> 01:21:52.639
to see if we can identify
these patterns going or not.

01:21:52.639 --> 01:21:53.930
I think some of them are there.

01:21:53.930 --> 01:21:54.590
Others are not.

01:21:54.590 --> 01:21:57.990
So we'll see how good they
are in their strategy.

01:21:57.990 --> 01:22:01.990
Ask tough questions and that
I wanted to do more guidance,

01:22:01.990 --> 01:22:02.995
but I talk a lot.

